==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oersted
<hw>Oer"sted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[After <person>Hans
Christian <etsep>Oersted</etsep></person>, Danish physicist.]</ety>
<fld>(Elec.)</fld> <def>The C. G. S. unit of magnetic reluctance or
resistance, equal to the reluctance of a centimeter cube of air (or
vacuum) between parallel faces. Also, a reluctance in which unit
magnetomotive force sets up unit flux.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

